		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Phil.</placeName> <date>July 28&#47;56</date></p>
				<p>Revd Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed please find<lb/> my check for &#36;25.  Endeavour to secure<lb/> the Book <persName>Mrs Arnold</persName> spoke of<lb/> the name of which I have forgotten</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Yours truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Mayer Arnold</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">pr Sna<add>&#63;</add></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p>Find also &#36;25 from me the object for<lb/> which it is&#44; is expressed in the list whereon<lb/> my name is signed&#44; namely&#44; to distribute the<lb/> amt in cheap bibles as you may deem proper<lb/> and I wish it to be considered an unusual<lb/> subscription subject to such increase as<lb/> I may feel able to afford.  Let me know the<lb/> amt of <persName>Moses Gimbel&#39;s</persName> &#40;of <placeName>Vincennes</placeName>&#41; debt<lb/> he is here for a few days &#38; wishes to pay &#38; if<lb/> you will leave a list of such of our custom</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p>ers as owe you I will endeavor<lb/> to collect same&#44; as I know you are<lb/> too lenient &#38; perhaps careless in such<lb/> matters.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Your friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><add>&#63;</add> <persName role="author">M Arnold</persName></p>
		</body>
